{"tid":2214620,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓，你飲水未","createTime":"2020-09-23T11:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T11:20:49.000Z","uid":343779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6504ece381d5afc9be8146e89837ca5348f7f9cf","tid":2214620,"uid":343779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T11:19:09.000Z","msg":"本身已經有水機俾貓貓用<br />\n不過我見網上有人分享只要將個水擺喺屋企正中間或者佢平時成日去嘅地方<br />\n啲貓貓都會自己走去飲水<br />\n試過都係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放喺枱面又推落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放喺地下又去玩水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦一杯唔夠擺夠兩杯<br />\n都係唔飲 仲整到成地水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱我個水機filter要換<br />\n我兩日都未出去買 (係我錯一陣買）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住頂住檔冇乜嘢事<br />\n點知佢就唔飲水！<br />\n咁我就成個filter拆出嚟 又唔飲！<br />\n換水換左幾次 水機都洗咗幾次<br />\n冇咗個filter 佢真係飲都唔飲！<br />\n唔通佢係傳說中嘅品水師！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通佢唔飲地下嗰兩杯水係因為我屋企冇過濾器<br />\n<br />\n買過雞骨粉溝水 失敗<br />\n自己整雞柳 有雞汁 失敗 <br />\n買咗怪獸部落湯罐 成功，不過唔肯咬肉肉 罐罐都淨係飲湯 好敗家<br />\n<br />\n準備試：<br />\n貓奶粉<br />\n雞湯包<br />\n買魔力碗<br />\n屋企加濾水器<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有啲咩方法可以令到佢飲多啲水"},{"pid":"58e32b46ec4d7cc84d6ced9d0964ffc1b9a9ae43","tid":2214620,"uid":261849,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"貓貓相 <br />\n我幫你動物傳心<br />\n<br />\n我個隻自動自覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完糧就飲 無特別教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23639cfe92be68679b3a6a2c6e7c644f22f34e60","tid":2214620,"uid":46457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"你有幾多隻貓？<br />\n我有一隻又係仆街仔，轉新水機唔撚飲水<br />\n後尾見到第二隻貓飲完水，自己就八八卦卦用隻肥掌試味，依家成日玩完水就飲水"},{"pid":"9d214e40eeececa34c714a5d86688511bb30a4f2","tid":2214620,"uid":343779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e32b46ec4d7cc84d6ced9d0964ffc1b9a9ae43","tid":2214620,"uid":261849,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"貓貓相 <br />\n我幫你動物傳心<br />\n<br />\n我個隻自動自覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完糧就飲 無特別教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:27:35.000Z","msg":"真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8e25a6cc29cff449c68ad4761c05affd00818c","tid":2214620,"uid":343779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23639cfe92be68679b3a6a2c6e7c644f22f34e60","tid":2214620,"uid":46457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"你有幾多隻貓？<br />\n我有一隻又係仆街仔，轉新水機唔撚飲水<br />\n後尾見到第二隻貓飲完水，自己就八八卦卦用隻肥掌試味，依家成日玩完水就飲水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:28:13.000Z","msg":"我得一隻<br />\n我就係試水個隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd76f1842a6af602e62d00367269ba5b6aaf41bb","tid":2214620,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:30:23.000Z","msg":"飲隻貓"},{"pid":"be1b67457b83d6033bee2bff6232f6023a0ba97a","tid":2214620,"uid":224213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:30:42.000Z","msg":"示範一次俾佢睇"},{"pid":"d6c1b0e203bca2768a04685c424cfc9f0ec7f068","tid":2214620,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:32:30.000Z","msg":"冇相點幫你傳心"},{"pid":"7fb142b34154a049b011082cec83e12b591d670b","tid":2214620,"uid":343779,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"be1b67457b83d6033bee2bff6232f6023a0ba97a","tid":2214620,"uid":224213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sco