i\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就晚晚望住個白痴咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1547db919260f5684ed1e61a77d7faae6952c50d","tid":2214620,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"肯食濕糧已經補好多水<br />\n我隻貓大個左唔太中意食濕<br />\n可能食厭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e1bdd42e283df29318e1258273beb11f90c6b0","tid":2214620,"uid":343779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1547db919260f5684ed1e61a77d7faae6952c50d","tid":2214620,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"肯食濕糧已經補好多水<br />\n我隻貓大個左唔太中意食濕<br />\n可能食厭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"濕糧我最多只可以加少少水<br />\n多兩滴佢都唔肯食<br />\n<br />\n日間大部份時間因為返工佢都係要食乾糧<br />\n以前食完乾糧都會飲水<br />\n而家飲都唔飲<br />\n好鬼擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢係鍾意食乾糧多個濕糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0678af9d857d2ace6d17aa4d30a8c6669c3014f6","tid":2214620,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:36:48.000Z","msg":"我果隻會俾佢食食下乾糧中途加水<br />\n佢又會乖乖地食濕咗既乾糧"},{"pid":"26b447cd6362c871366f70a6772c7ee797fdf32f","tid":2214620,"uid":253451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:40:43.000Z","msg":"我嗰時換新水機，或者放碗喺枱之後，會捉貓貓去碗/水機前面，然後用手指點一點裡面啲水，然後掂落佢個鼻度，佢就會飲咗嗰滴水，同埋伸頭去飲。有時佢鍾意舐我隻手上嘅水，我就會用手引導佢飲水"},{"pid":"d744320f731c27c8c90b904788b1d09e706aca41","tid":2214620,"uid":9006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"濕糧加水<br />\n應該穩陣啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ceba6575f7f41a8a0f8ad42d2f